## <FONT COLOR = Cyan>嵌套循环</font>

### <FONT COLOR = PowderBlue size = 4>100以内的素数</font>

```c
int x = 2 ;
int i = 2 ;
int Prime = 1 ;
while( x < 100 ){
	while( i < x ){
		if( x % i == 0){
			Prime = 0 ;
			break ;
		}
